info.author: Jaakko Salli
classifiers: Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows :: Windows NT/2000
info.description:
wxPropertyGrid is a specialized grid for editing properties such as
strings, numbers, flag sets, string arrays, and colours. Component was originally
made for C++ wxWidgets, but the wxPython bindings include some Python-specific
customizations as well.
info.name: wxPropertyGrid
info.summary: A property sheet control for wxWidgets/wxPython
